        "genprov_section_title":"Applicability; description of the phosphorus production subcategory",
        "genprov_desc":"(Subpart A) The provisions of this subpart are applicable to discharges of pollutants resulting from the production of phosphorus and ferrophosphorus by smelting of phosphate ore.",
