        "genprov_section_title":"Applicability; description of the slag processing subcategory",
        "genprov_desc":"(Subpart C) The provisions of this subpart are applicable to discharges resulting from slag processing, wherein: (a) The residual metallic values in the furnace slag are recovered via concentration for return to the furnace, or (b) the slag is \"shotted\" for other further use.",
