        "genprov_section_title":"Applicability; description of the oil-base solvent wash paint subcategory",
        "genprov_desc":"(Subpart A) The provisions of this subpart are applicable to discharges resulting from the production of oil-base paint where the tank cleaning is performed using solvents. When a plant is subject to effluent limitations covering more than one subcategory the discharge limitation shall be the aggregate of the limitations applicable to the total production covered in each subcategory.",
